ComicInfo.Summary:
Still ILL Comics invites you to join them in this self-publication of epic proportions! Brian Pulido's Lady Death vs. Dan Mendoza's Zombie Tramp. Indulge in this labor of love. Written and drawn entirely by Dan Mendoza with Supervision and Blessings from Brian Pulido. This 64 Page perfect bound book contains 56 Pages of epic story with colors by The Xong Brothers, Carlos Moreno D and Dan Mendoza. Rated Mature.
Bored with their mastery of dream realms, a mischievous force looks to be entertained. With the help of her companion, She scratches into alternate realities. Pulling through two representations of death and forces them to face off. Who will make it out alive? Can These two survive a realm they can't control?
